t="v1" itunes:key="L17">Two policemen in the car behind</p><p begin="02:57.887" end="03:06.131" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18">Not on duty but they stopped</p><p begin="03:06.131" end="03:17.350" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19">And just before the car caught fire</p><p begin="03:17.350" end="03:25.771" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20">Bravely they pulled her off</p><p begin="03:25.771" end="03:34.246" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21">Bravely they pulled her off</p><p begin="03:34.246" end="03:42.647" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22">Bravely they pulled her off</p><p begin="03:42.647" end="03:51.039" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23">Bravely they pulled her off</p><p begin="03:51.039" end="03:56.016" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24">If I were you Chrissie I'd rather</p></div></body></tt>